name: Farruko
description: '''Carlos Efrén Reyes Rosado''' (born May 2, 1991), known professionally as '''Farruko''', is a Puerto Rican singer. He rose to fame collaborating with [[Daddy Yankee]], [[J Balvin]], [[Don Omar]], and [[J Álvarez]]. He came to prominence in 2010 with his first solo album, ''El Talento del Bloque''.
